      <description>&lt;p&gt;This is the first project I was hired to do visual effects and compositing all on my own. I designed interfaces, animated them, and composited them into the scene using through a combination of various methods including rotoscoping and color keying.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;project-image&#34;&gt;
  &lt;video width=&#34;960&#34; height=&#34;540&#34; autoplay loop muted controls&gt;
    
      &lt;source src=&#34;http://bluevisual.tv/videos/cybervice-video-01.mp4&#34; /&gt;
    
  &lt;/video&gt;
  
&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Me and the client discussed different ways to do things, and I was given a lot of creative freedom, which was really nice. I really felt in my element too because I love computers and they&amp;rsquo;re an important part of my life. My interest in this allowed to have insightful artistic direction and believeable content.&lt;/p&gt;

